,\\\"span\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"pricing-faq-toggle\\\",\\\"aria-hidden\\\":\\\"true\\\"}]]}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"p\\\",null,{\\\"children\\\":\\\"Never. Loglime charges zero commission on every order your restaurant takes through its own app, on every plan and at every volume level. Payment goes directly to the restaurant payment gateway account. Loglime does not sit between the restaurant and the customer payment.\\\"}]]}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"details\\\",\\\"What is the early access offer?\\\",{\\\"className\\\":\\\"pricing-faq-item\\\",\\\"open\\\":false,\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"summary\\\",null,{\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"span\\\",null,{\\\"children\\\":\\\"What is the early access offer?\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"span\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"pricing-faq-toggle\\\",\\\"aria-hidden\\\":\\\"true\\\"}]]}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"p\\\",null,{\\\"children\\\":\\\"The first 10 independent restaurants receive 50% off standard setup pricing. Starter drops from $298 to $149, Business from $498 to $249 and Pro from $798 to $399. Early access closes when those spots are taken, and standard pricing applies after that.\\\"}]]}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"details\\\",\\\"Can I upgrade my plan later?\\\",{\\\"className\\\":\\\"pricing-faq-item\\\",\\\"open\\\":false,\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"summary\\\",null,{\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"span\\\",null,{\\\"children\\\":\\\"Can I upgrade my plan later?\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"span\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"pricing-faq-toggle\\\",\\\"aria-hidden\\\":\\\"true\\\"}]]}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"p\\\",null,{\\\"children\\\":\\\"Yes. A restaurant can upgrade from Starter to Business or Pro later and pay only the difference while early access pricing is active: $100 from Starter to Business, $250 from Starter to Pro and $150 from Business to Pro.\\\"}]]}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"details\\\",\\\"What do I need to pay Apple and Google?\\\",{\\\"className\\\":\\\"pricing-faq-item\\\",\\\"open\\\":false,\\\"children\\\":[\\\"$L43\\\",\\\"$L44\\\"]}