gle and belong to the restaurant.\"}]\n2e:[\"$\",\"details\",\"What happens if I do not renew the $49 maintenance fee?\",{\"className\":\"pricing-faq-item\",\"open\":false,\"children\":[[\"$\",\"summary\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"children\":\"What happens if I do not renew the $49 maintenance fee?\"}],[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"pricing-faq-toggle\",\"aria-hidden\":\"true\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"The app continues to run and customers can keep ordering. The restaurant simply loses access to Loglime support, minor updates and technical assistance. The maintenance fee is optional.\"}]]}]\n2f:[\"$\",\"details\",\"Are there any per-order fees from Loglime?\",{\"className\":\"pricing-faq-item\",\"open\":false,\"children\":[[\"$\",\"summary\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"children\":\"Are there any per-order fees from Loglime?\"}],[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"pricing-faq-toggle\",\"aria-hidden\":\"true\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"No. Loglime charges zero per-order fees and zero transaction fees. Standard payment gateway processing fees, such as Stripe fees, are paid directly to the payment gateway.\"}]]}]\n30:[\"$\",\"details\",\"Is Starter really a complete app?\",{\"className\":\"pricing-faq-item\",\"open\":false,\"children\":[[\"$\",\"summary\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"children\":\"Is Starter really a complete app?\"}],[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"pricing-faq-toggle\",\"aria-hidden\":\"true\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"Yes. Starter includes branded iOS and Android apps, direct ordering, admin dashboard, menu customization, customer login, order tracking, push notifications, supported payment gateways, analytics, logo design, launch kit, technical setup and support.\"}]]}]\n31:[\"$\",\"details\",\"What makes Pro different?\",{\"className\":\"pricing-faq-item\",\"open\":false,\"children\":[[\"$\",\"summary\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"children\":\"What makes Pro different?\"}],[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"pricing-faq-toggle\",\"aria-hidden\":\"true\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"Pro adds full source code ownership, AI sales insights, demand forecasting, AI menu recommendations, an AI ordering chatbot, unlimited multi-branch support, priority support and a 100% white-label experience with no Loglime mention anywhere.\"}]]}]\n32:[\"$\",\"details\",\"Is there a free trial?\",{\"className\":\"pricing-faq-item\",\"open\":false,\"children\":[[\"$\",\"summary\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"children\":\"Is there a free trial?\"}],[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"pricing-faq-toggle\",\"aria-hidden\":\"true\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"There is no free trial because each restaurant app is configured around that restaurant brand, menu and business details. Instead, restaurants can book a demo and review the full app flow before committing.\"}]]}]\n33:[\"$\",\"details\",\"Cuanto cuesta Loglime para restaurantes en Estados Unidos?\",{\"className\":\"pricing-faq-item\",\"open\":false,\"children\":[[\"$\",\"summary\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"children\":\"Cuanto cuesta Loglime para restaurantes en Estados Unidos?\"}],[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"pricing-faq-toggle\",\"aria-hidden\":\"true\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"Loglime ofrece acceso anticipado desde $149 de pago unico para Starter, sin mensualidades ni comision por pedido. Business cuesta $249 y Pro cuesta $399 durante acceso anticipado. Todos los planes incluyen apps iOS y Android con la marca del restaurante.\"}]]}]\n36:null\n37:[\"$\",\"h4\",null,{\"children\":\"Table booking system\"}]\n38:[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"Customers book tables directly through your branded app. You confirm or decline requests from the dashboard and customers receive automated status updates.\"}]\n39:[\"$\",\"div\",\"Loyalty and offers programme\",{\"className\":\"pricing-detail-item\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h4\",null,{\"children\":\"Loyalty and offers programme\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"Create promotional offers, discount codes and repeat-guest rewards from the admin dashboard, then push them to customers who already have your app installed.\"}]]}]\n3a:[\"$\",\"div\",\"WhatsApp integration\",{\"className\":\"pricing-detail-item\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h4\",null,{\"children\":\"WhatsApp integration\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"Send order status notifications and marketing broadcasts through WhatsApp so the restaurant owns a direct customer communication channel.\"}]]}]\n3b:[\"$\",\"div\",\"Rider and delivery management app\",{\"className\":\"pricing-detail-item\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h4\",null,{\"children\":\"Rider and delivery management app\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"Delivery riders get a dedicated app to accept deliveries, see navigation, update availability, view delivery history and share live status with the restaurant.\"}]]}]\n3c:[\"$\",\"div\",\"Multi-branch support\",{\"className\":\"pricing-detail-item\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h4\",null,{\"children\":\"Multi-branch support\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"Manage up to three restaurant locations from one dashboard while keeping each branch menu, queue, revenue and analytics separate.\"}]]}]\n3d:[\"$\",\"article\",\"Pro-details\",{\"className\":\"pricing-detail-card\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"pricing-detail-head\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"children\":\"Pro\"}],[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"children\":[\"Pro\",\" full feature breakdown\"]}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"Full ownership package\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"pricing-detail-grid\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",\"Everything in Business\",{\"className\":\"pricing-detail-item\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h4\",null,{\"children\":\"Everything in Business\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"Pro includes every Business feature: direct ordering, booking, loyalty, WhatsApp, delivery management and multi-branch operations.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",\"AI sales insights and demand forecasting\",{\"className\":\"pricing-detail-item\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h4\",null,{\"children\":\"AI sales insights and demand forecasting\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"The app analyzes order data and surfaces specific recommendations: what to promote, when to run offers, which hours are strongest and where demand is likely to rise.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",\"AI menu recommendations\",{\"className\":\"pricing-detail-item\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h4\",null,{\"children\":\"AI menu recommendations\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"Customers see item suggestions based on order history, time of day, popular trends and seasonal behavior, helping increase average order value.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",\"AI ordering chatbot\",{\"className\":\"pricing-detail-item\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h4\",null,{\"children\":\"AI ordering chatbot\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"A built-in ordering assistant answers menu questions, guides customers through choices and reduces friction that causes abandoned carts.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",\"Full source code ownership\",{\"className\":\"pricing-detail-item\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h4\",null,{\"children\":\"Full source code ownership\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"The complete iOS app, Android app and admin dashboard source code is delivered to you. You can self-host, modify, extend or hand it to another developer.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",\"100% white-label\",{\"className\":\"pricing-detail-item\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h4\",null,{\"children\":\"100% white-label\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"No Loglime mention inside the app, notifications, emails or app store listing metadata. Customers know only your restaurant brand.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",\"Unlimited multi-branch and priority support\",{\"className\":\"pricing-detail-item\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h4\",null,{\"children\":\"Unlimited multi-branch and priority support\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"Scale beyond three locations, get a dedicated setup manager and move support requests above the standard queue.\"}]]}]]}]]}]\n3e:[\"$\",\"td\",null,{\"children\":\"Automated push notifications\"}]\n3f:[\"$\",\"td\",null,{\"children\":[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"pricing-table-check\",\"aria-label\":\"Included\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"$L13\",null,{\"iconNode\":\"$3:props:children:props:children:5:props:children:0:props:children:0:props:iconNode\",\"className\":\"lucide-check\",\"size\":16}]}]}]\n40:[\"$\",\"td\",null,{\"className\":\"pricing-featured-col\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"pricing-table-check\",\"aria-label\":\"Included\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"$L13\",null,{\"iconNode\":\"$3:props:children:props:children:5:props:children:0:props:children:0:props:iconNode\",\"className\":\"lucide-check\",\"size\":16}]}]}]\n41:[\"$\",\"td\",null,{\"children\":[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"pricing-table-check\",\"aria-label\":\"Included\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"$L13\",null,{\"iconNode\":\"$3:props:children:props:children:5:props:children:0:props:children:0:props:iconNode\",\"className\":\"lucide-check\",\"size\":16}]}]}]\n42:[\"$\",\"tr\",\"Ordering and customer experience-One-tap reorder\",{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"td\",null,{\"children\":\"One-tap reorder\"}],[\"$\",\"td\",null,{\"children\":[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"pricing-table-check\",\"aria-label\":\"Included\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"$L13\",null,{\"iconNode\":\"$3:props:children:props:children:5:props:children:0:props:children:0:props:iconNode\",\"className\":\"lucide-check\",\"size\":16}]}]}],[\"$\",\"td\",null,{\"className\":\"pricing-featured-col\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"pricing-table-check\",\"aria-label\":\"Included\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"$L13\",null,{\"iconNode\":\"$3:props:children:props:children:5:props:children:0:props:children:0:props:iconNode\",\"className\":\"lucide-